Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,失物近在咫尺 克洛伊同學怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,波瀾雖興亦將止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這是說最後會有好事發生對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,聖誕節那時候正是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊 那明年肯定也會有好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要到明年了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,十 九
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這之前我拜託你告訴我你的煩惱 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我又有了個願望 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要明年也和克洛伊同學一起祝福新年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要拍咯

